/svg></div></div><div class="flex-1 flex items-center gap-1 min-w-0 pb-2 "><p class="text-[14px] leading-[150%] grow wrap-anywhere text-heading">Built your app</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="border-t border-outline-secondary my-4"></div><div class="flex flex-col"><div class="flex items-start gap-2"><div class="flex-1 flex items-center gap-1 min-w-0 pt-0.5"><p class="text-[12px] leading-[150%] grow wrap-anywhere text-body font-semibold uppercase">What I did</p></div></div><div class="mt-2 chatMarkdown"><div class="wmde-markdown wmde-markdown-color rounded [&amp;_li]:!text-[14px] [&amp;_li]:!leading-[24px] [&amp;_li]:!mb-2 [&amp;_ul]:!list-disc [&amp;_ol]:!list-decimal [&amp;_ul]:!pl-4 [&amp;_ol]:!pl-4"><ul>
<li>Built complete XUBA' restaurant landing page with 8 sections: Hero, Nosotros, Menú (4 tabs), Reservaciones, Galería, Redes Sociales + QR, Ubicación y Footer</li>
<li>Implemented full visual identity with Playfair Display + Montserrat fonts, terracota/esmeralda/naranja color palette, animated tabs, reservation form with validation, and QR code generator</li>
<li>Added floating WhatsApp button with pulse animation, scroll-to-top button, IntersectionObserver animations, responsive navbar with hamburger menu, and Google Maps embed for Polanco CDMX</li>
